{"title":"草原行","authors":["布赫"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布赫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"察右中旗辉腾锡勒旅游区"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花似锦草蓊茸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风送爽鸟唱鸣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘盛装捧哈达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年乘马路旁迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乳色毡包彩旗艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧草葳蕤没牛群；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬酒歌声盈天际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清香奶茶待来人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风电场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色风轮高空旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勃勃生机注草原；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色能源始开发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西电东送增奉献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉腾锡勒①换新颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红白蓝花绽遍野；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农户牧家电灯照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞上今朝无夜天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注①：辉腾锡勒系蒙语，意为“寒冷的山梁”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凉城县岱海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山花烂熳树叶青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅人泛舟游湖中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天蓝水碧成一体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知船在水上在昊空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中塘温泉宜人浴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岱海鱼虾有盛名；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天造地设风光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不次江南沿海城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤峰市阿斯哈图②冰石林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石险峻势雄伟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似人似物岿然立；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远看近睹形态变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琪花瑶草更增奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石林石海走马鹿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白桦树丛野鸟栖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神工鬼斧铸地貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诿与今人几多谜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注②：阿斯哈图，蒙语意为“险峻的岩石”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原城市——锡林浩特"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敖包山下彩云翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱甍碧瓦崭新房；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡林广场阔如海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大气清新草木香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银鹏展翅通北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陆路成网达四方；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活跨入快车道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人策马奔小康。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡水悠悠恋故土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百灵润喉颂家乡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看草原日出时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地处处披霞光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的锡林浩特，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多情的草原城，你是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩瀚大地上的一颗红宝石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万顷绿原中的一枝郁金香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人高举着双手为你祝福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌手拉着马头琴为你歌唱。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}